D.U.N.K.L.E.R
Planty

is a 3D first-person planting simulator :)

The goal is to remove the purple fog by planting. More seeds are hidden in
the city around you. 

Try to find out what happend here!

This game was developed within Gametalente 2022. We had one week to finish the
game. It was a lot of fun! (At least I had)
